{"id":5336,"date":"2026-01-23T03:15:34","date_gmt":"2026-01-23T03:15:34","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.npackpm.com\/?page_id=5336"},"modified":"2026-01-24T02:02:43","modified_gmt":"2026-01-24T02:02:43","slug":"deodorant-filling-machine","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.npackpm.com\/deodorant-filling-machine","title":{"rendered":"Deodorant filling machine"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-page\" data-elementor-id=\"5336\" class=\"elementor elementor-5336\" data-elementor-post-type=\"page\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-656de7b0 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"656de7b0\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-99354b4 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"99354b4\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-15e2db4e elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"15e2db4e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\"> Automatic deodorant filling machine<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2bec6fdf elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"2bec6fdf\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3bc5def7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"3bc5def7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Npack deodorant filling machine is one type of filling equipement, which adapts with advance hot filling technology,the working process is typically hot-fill,the solid formula is melted, then dispensed into the empty stick barrel, after filling,a cooling station(cooling tunnel) solidifies it before capping. Precise volume control is usually achieved with a piston filler.The piston is also driven by a servo motor.<\/p><p>The machine designed for faste changeovers between different container sizes and product lines;Easy operation and cleaning.It is suitable for filling hot liquid or viscous liquid.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2e6fd310 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"2e6fd310\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-211b2ccb elementor-widget elementor-widget-video\" data-id=\"211b2ccb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;youtube_url&quot;:&quot;https:\\\/\\\/youtu.be\\\/jo0OqbwteRc&quot;,&quot;show_image_overlay&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;image_overlay&quot;:{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https:\\\/\\\/www.npackpm.com\\\/wp-content\\\/uploads\\\/2025\\\/10\\\/2025101510050893.webp&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:2803,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;tube filling and sealing machine&quot;,&quot;source&quot;:&quot;library&quot;},&quot;video_type&quot;:&quot;youtube&quot;,&quot;controls&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"video.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-wrapper elementor-open-inline\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-video\"><\/div>\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-custom-embed-image-overlay\" style=\"background-image: url(https:\/\/www.npackpm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/2025101510050893.webp);\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-custom-embed-play\" role=\"button\" aria-label=\"\u64ad\u653e\u6709\u5173\u7684\u89c6\u9891 tube filling and sealing machine\"